    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make sadism a criminal offence",
        "additional_details": "The crime will have a maximum sentence of 5 years imprisonment and will be classed in 3 rungs.\r\n\r\nRung A - max 5 years custody\r\nPerforming mental torture or depraved acts for a sadistic cause.\r\n\r\nRung B - max 2 years custody\r\nHarming someone's mental or physical health in order to gain pleasure.\r\n\r\nRung C - max 6 months custody\r\nGetting pleasure from the reaction or suffering of a person who has been mentally or physically harmed.",
        "background": "This petition asks the government to create a new criminal offence called\r\n 'Causing suffering for a sadistic cause'.\r\nThe act will cover all cases in which somebody deliberately physically or mentally harms a person in an unprovoked attack and then gets pleasure from their reaction/ suffering.",
